Please contact the BZFlag developers if there are any questions or
concerns regarding existing fonts, the addition of new fonts, or
modifications.  All fonts included in BZFlag must be freely modifiable
and freely redistributable.

http://sourceforge.net/projects/dejavu/files/dejavu/2.25/dejavu-fonts-ttf-2.25.tar.bz2
is the source for the Deja Vu font files here, which were extracted
from that upstream file.
